To Factorial a Number with number named facNumber
    Make number named counter
    Set counter to 1
    Set Number to 1
    Loop counter <= facNumber
        Set Number to Number * counter
        Set counter to counter + 1

To Run
    Print with "Factorial"
    Print with "---------"
    Make number named tenFac
    Make number named fiveFac
    Factorial tenFac with 10
    Print with tenFac
    Factorial fiveFac with 5
    Print with fiveFac
    